msgstr ""
"// 오류! `private_funciton`은 사적인 함수입니다.\n"
"    //rarry::private_funciton();\n"

#: src/cargo.md:3
msgid ""
"`cargo` is the official Rust package management tool. It has lots of really "
"useful features to improve code quality and developer velocity! These "
