"// By reversing the types, we end up implementing non-commutative addition.\n"
"// Here, we make `Add<Foo>` - the trait for addition with a RHS of type `Foo`.\n"
"// This block implements the operation: Bar + Foo = BarFoo\n"
msgstr ""
